{"tid":1940341,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"撞返班舊朋友，發現自己原來因為idol改變左好多","createTime":"2020-03-23T17:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T02:25:18.000Z","uid":87394,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d84b74a6e1ae70bd16de8bc97d55b26f7f6b45","tid":1940341,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"呢班本身都係d酒肉朋友黎<br />\n唔係好交心，但有期都玩得好埋<br />\n今日收工撞到佢地叫我去食餐飯<br />\n咁耐冇見聚下舊都ok，但其實我比較想返屋企睇live..<br />\n成餐飯個話題離不開前排屌左邊條女，遲下想屌邊條女，完全搭唔到嘴<br />\n又問我呢排係咪收心養性？我都只係微笑敷衍過去<br />\n其實都無講錯，我的確因為著迷於她，其他人都再無興趣<br />\n飯後我都即刻話有野做自己走先，我諗佢地都唔會再想搵我玩<br />\n奇怪既係，我居然完全唔懷念以前既生活，甚至覺得噁心<br />\n我只可以講 追星的孩子不會壞 idol真係可以導人向善🙏🏻"},{"pid":"6c8cb8f94ba75c830c03d7290f92aa8a9ac0636d","tid":1940341,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"樓主勁warm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ec16a3af1868874d62c4e2ce331ce0ccb02bd8","tid":1940341,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c8cb8f94ba75c830c03d7290f92aa8a9ac0636d","tid":1940341,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"樓主勁warm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:07:14.000Z","msg":"咁快？有冇認真睇架"},{"pid":"0e19fb37318a3158f93a5c2bb511c272b55847dd","tid":1940341,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90ec16a3af1868874d62c4e2ce331ce0ccb02bd8","tid":1940341,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c8cb8f94ba75c830c03d7290f92aa8a9ac0636d","tid":1940341,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"樓主勁warm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:07:14.000Z","msg":"咁快？有冇認真睇架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:07:57.000Z","msg":"我一目十行 再世孔子"},{"pid":"fd4e7baeae4fa64112c88da92a518b0721ac5c61","tid":1940